<div class="text-justify">The term Ayush represents age and anyone, who wants to live a healthy life can focus on performing certain rituals. Ayush homa is primarily meant for increasing the life span of a person by reducing health disorders. It plays a key role in improving life standards by minimizing health ailments. The main objective of Ayush homa is to seek the blessings from Ayur Devta, the God of life.</div>
<div>&nbsp;</div>
<div class="text-justify">Ayush homa can be performed on birthdays based on the stars. One can also conduct this homa at the correct time after analyzing the birth chart. Ayush homam provides methods for clearing the negative effects of previous birth, which in turn helps improve the overall well-being of a person. In addition, it is possible to control untimely and sudden death with this homam by developing the quality of life. Those who want relief from mental and physical health problems can organize Ayush homa for living a better life and to reduce the bad effects of planets to minimize accidents, injuries and major health threats. Performing this Yagna once a year, bestows on you with the power and supremacy to fulfill and attain success. Lord of age ‘Aayur Devatha’ is invoked during this homam. This homam is specially focused on the children, who remain constantly ill or suffer any type of ailment. This homam rejuvenates one’s life by reducing health disorders. Ayush Homa is also a remedy to people, who are born under ‘Balarishta Yoga’ in their horoscope.</div>
