                <div class="text-justify">KALI POOJA is a fervent prayer to the fearsome, ferocious Goddess. The aim of Kali Puja is to seek the help of Maa Kali in destroying evil, both in the outside world and within us. that Kali Puja is performed to diminish ego and all negative tendencies that hamper spiritual growth.
				</div>
