        <div id="collapseThree5" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree5" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">TULSI POOJA Tulsi is a sacred plant which can be found in almost every Hindu home. Tulsi Puja or worship of the Tulsi plant is performed, almost every day.</div>
            </div>
