                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree53" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree53" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">MAHAGANAPATHI HOMAM Performing Ganapathy Homam at least once in a year will bestow prosperity, health, wealth and peace of mind to the individual. Ganapathy Homam should be performed on all auspicious occasions before starting a new project or grihapravesham or getting married or to remove obstacles.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree54">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree54"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree54">
