            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree54" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree54" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">PITHRU SHANTHI HOMAM Pithru Karyiam or Oblations are done for the peace of the departed souls. Homam is done in the name of Athma, name and star of the deceased person to give mukthi or salvation to the souls of deceased parents, relatives and ancestors. The performer of the homam gets relieved of all adverse effects due to the restlessness of the souls and curse of forefathers.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree55">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree55"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree55">
                <span class="d-inline-block f-size-18 rt-hw-40 bg-gradient-primary rt-circle rt-mr-10 text-center text-white"><i
                        class="icofont-support-faq"></i></span>
					NAVAGRAHA HOMAM…105
                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree55" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree55" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">NAVAGRAHA HOMAM This homam has the power to counter flaws in the horoscope and enables a person to prosper in life in case astrological defects are the main blocks to his well-being and appease the nine planets i.e. the Sun, Moon, Mars, Mercury, Jupiter, Venus, Saturn, Rahu and Ketu. Sun for health, Moon for success, Mars for wealth, Mercury for knowledge, Jupiter for education, Venus for art and music, Saturn for happiness and confidence, Rahu for strength and Ketu for prosperity.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree56">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree56"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree56">
                <span class="d-inline-block f-size-18 rt-hw-40 bg-gradient-primary rt-circle rt-mr-10 text-center text-white"><i
                        class="icofont-support-faq"></i></span>
					CHANDI HOMAM…105
                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree56" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree56" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">CHANDI HOMAM Chandi Homam is performed to remove any obstacles or blocks in growth – both internally and externally and the sufferings resulting from poison, sorcery, thieves etc. By performing Chandi homam, one can attain health, wealth, prosperity, fame, success, strength, prevent ailments, danger and avoid defeat in the hand of adversaries.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree57">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree57"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree57">
                <span class="d-inline-block f-size-18 rt-hw-40 bg-gradient-primary rt-circle rt-mr-10 text-center text-white"><i
                        class="icofont-support-faq"></i></span>
					AYUSH HOMAM…105
                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree57" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree57" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">AYUSH HOMAM This Homam is performed to Lord Shiva to ensure longevity in life. The best remedy is to perform Ayush Homam on every birthday, as reckoned by the tamil birth-star and not by the English birth date, which can help avoid untimely and unfortunate death. </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree58">
