                <span class="d-inline-block f-size-18 rt-hw-40 bg-gradient-primary rt-circle rt-mr-10 text-center text-white"><i
                        class="icofont-support-faq"></i></span>
						HOMAMS TO GET MARRIED…105
                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree6" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree6" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">HOMAMS TO GET MARRIED Homams can also be performed for people who want to get married and remove any obstacles that are delaying marriage. The bride or groom will be blessed with a suitable spouse and enjoy a good relationship. Those who have kuja dosha i.e bad position of Mars in their natal chart can perform this homam and nullify the effects of the planets.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree61">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
