                        class="icofont-support-faq"></i></span>
					ABHYANKARA HOMAM…105
                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree62" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree62" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">ABHYANKARA HOMAM strengthens the mind and removes fear. The presiding deity Indra-Abhyankara is appeased with the offering of ghee, Havis, cooked rice and Special Sticks known as samith in the fire.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree63">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
