                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree63" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree63" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">SUDARSHANA HOMAM The Sudarshana Chakram is the mighty weapon of Lord Narayana and has many auspicious attributes associated with it. “Pida Pradanam” which gives immediate relief from pain and suffering, “Papa Nashanam”, the destruction of sins.  Performing Sudarshana Homam confers health, wealth and prosperity and bestows spirituality.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree64">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree64"
                    aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree64">
                <span class="d-inline-block f-size-18 rt-hw-40 bg-gradient-primary rt-circle rt-mr-10 text-center text-white"><i
                        class="icofont-support-faq"></i></span>
					MAHALAKSHMI HOMAM…105
                </button>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <div id="collapseThree64" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree64" data-parent="#accordion">
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="text-justify">MAHALAKSHMI HOMAM Lakshmi is the Goddess of wealth and prosperity, and is the divine spouse of Lord Vishnu. The worship of Lakshmi brings about prosperity with a sense of responsibility.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- end single accrodian -->
	<div class="card wow fade-in-bottom" data-wow-duration="1.5s">
        <div class="card-header card-primary" id="headingThree65">
            <h5 class="mb-0">
                <button class="btn btn-link collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree65"
